<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>hmmm\r\n:/dev/null!user@host PRIVMSG #lobby :+2 beans to Valware</title>
